public class WorldEdgeIdentifier extends com.telenav.mesakit.graph.identifiers.EdgeIdentifier
An edge identifier in a WorldGraph. Scopes an edge identifier with a WorldCell. The cell for this identifier can be retrieved with worldCell() and the edge (WorldEdge) with edge().
